      *! version 1.0.0  04oct2004
program define _growmiss
	version 6, missing

	gettoken type 0 : 0
	gettoken g    0 : 0
	gettoken eqs  0 : 0 

	syntax varlist [if] [in] [, BY(string)]
	if `"`by'"' != "" {
		_egennoby rowmiss() `"`by'"'
		/* NOTREACHED */
	}


	quietly { 
		tokenize `varlist'

		mac shift

		}
	}
